install/uninstall lfs/lvm on client machines

install
=======
select a command below for the target machines and replace with real ip addresses.

# for a800 machines
./store-deploy -f a800.yaml -n ip1[,ip2,..]

# for h800 machines
./store-deploy -f h800.yaml -n ip1[,ip2,..]

# for cpu machines
./store-deploy -f cpu.yaml -n ip1[,ip2,..]

uninstall
=========
select a command below for the target machines and replace with real ip addresses.

# for a800 machines
./store-deploy -u -f a800.yaml -n ip1[,ip2,..]

# for h800 machines
./store-deploy -u -f h800.yaml -n ip1[,ip2,..]

# for cpu machines
./store-deploy -u -f cpu.yaml -n ip1[,ip2,..]
